<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Medical NIW Initial Matrix | Public Lite</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --navy: #113a63;
      --navy-dark: #0a2642;
      --gold: #b88a2a;
      --gold-soft: #efe2bf;
      --bg: #f6f8fb;
      --card: #ffffff;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --line: #d7dee8;
      --ok: #0f766e;
      --warn: #9a3412;
      --danger: #991b1b;
      --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(17, 58, 99, 0.08);
      --radius: 18px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; }
    body { line-height: 1.55; }
    a { color: var(--navy); text-decoration: none; }
    .wrap { max-width: 1180px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px; }

    .brand {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy), var(--navy-dark));
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 28px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .brand::after {
      content: "LAW OFFICE OF HONG-MIN JUN";
      position: absolute;
      right: -10px;
      bottom: -10px;
      font-size: 34px;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      font-weight: 700;
      pointer-events: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .brand h1 { margin: 0 0 6px; font-size: 30px; }
    .brand .sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.86); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .brand .firm { font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .brand .contact { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88); font-size: 14px; }
    .brand .contact a { color: #fff; text-decoration: underline; }

    .toolbar {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin: 18px 0 22px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .toolbar-left, .toolbar-right {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .lang-toggle {
      display: inline-flex;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 4px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .lang-btn {
      border: 0;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--navy);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 9px 14px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .lang-btn[data-lang="en"].active { background: #123a63; color: #fff; }
    .lang-btn[data-lang="ko"].active { background: #0f766e; color: #fff; }
    .lang-btn[data-lang="zh"].active { background: #9a3412; color: #fff; }

    button {
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .15s ease, opacity .15s ease;
    }
    button:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-primary { background: var(--navy); color: #fff; }
    .btn-gold { background: var(--gold); color: #fff; }
    .btn-light { background: #fff; color: var(--navy); border: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .btn-danger { background: #fff; color: var(--danger); border: 1px solid #efc6c6; }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr 0.95fr;
      gap: 22px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .card-head {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(17,58,99,.05), rgba(17,58,99,.02));
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .card-head h2, .card-head h3 { margin: 0 0 6px; }
    .card-head p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; }
    .card-body { padding: 20px; }

    .section {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .section summary {
      list-style: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: #fafcff;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .section summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .section .inner { padding: 16px; }

    .fields { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }
    .fields-1 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 14px; }
    .fields-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 14px; }

    label { display: block; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; color: var(--navy-dark); }
    input, select, textarea {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 11px 12px;
      font-size: 14px;
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    textarea { min-height: 90px; resize: vertical; }

    .checklist { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 10px 14px; }
    .check {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      background: #fff;
      min-height: 54px;
    }
    .check input { width: 18px; height: 18px; margin-top: 2px; }
    .check span { font-size: 14px; }

    .score-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .score-box {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
    }
    .score-box .k { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .score-box .v { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--navy); }

    .pill {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: .3px;
    }
    .pill.ok { background: #dff5ef; color: var(--ok); }
    .pill.warn { background: #fff0dd; color: var(--warn); }
    .pill.danger { background: #fde9e9; color: var(--danger); }

    .report {
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      background: #fcfdff;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .report h3 { margin-top: 0; }
    .report p { margin: 8px 0; }
    .report ul { margin: 8px 0 0 18px; padding: 0; }

    .reserved-box {
      border: 1px dashed #d6dbe4;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fafbfe, #f7f9fc);
      color: var(--muted);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .reserved-box strong {
      display: block;
      color: var(--navy);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .note {
      border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
      background: #fffaf1;
      padding: 12px 14px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: #6c4c09;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .cta {
      margin-top: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(17,58,99,.05), rgba(17,58,99,.02));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 18px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .watermark {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 60px;
      color: rgba(17,58,99,0.035);
      transform: rotate(-28deg);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 3px;
      z-index: 0;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .wrap, .brand, .card { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .score-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
      .fields, .fields-3, .checklist { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    @media print {
      body { background: #fff; }
      .toolbar, .footer-note { display: none !important; }
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .section { break-inside: avoid; }
      .card { box-shadow: none; }
      .watermark { color: rgba(17,58,99,0.05); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="watermark">LAW OFFICE OF HONG-MIN JUN</div>

  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="brand">
      <div class="firm">Law Office of Hong-min Jun</div>
      <h1>Medical NIW Initial Matrix</h1>
      <div class="sub">Clinical → System Translation → Scalable Impact → National Importance</div>
      <div class="contact">
        Attorney for Foreign-Born Individuals and Small Business Owners · 12264 Lantern Rd, Fishers, IN 46038 · 317-701-2768 ·
        <a href="mailto:askus@junlawfirm.com">askus@junlawfirm.com</a> ·
        <a href="https://niw-junlawfirm.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">niw-junlawfirm.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="toolbar">
      <div class="toolbar-left">
        <button class="btn-primary" id="analyzeBtn">Generate Analysis</button>
        <button class="btn-gold" id="printBtn">Print / Save PDF</button>
        <button class="btn-light" id="sampleBtn">Load Sample</button>
        <button class="btn-danger" id="resetBtn">Reset</button>
      </div>
      <div class="toolbar-right">
        <div class="lang-toggle" aria-label="Language toggle">
          <button class="lang-btn active" type="button" data-lang="en" id="langEn">EN</button>
          <button class="lang-btn" type="button" data-lang="ko" id="langKo">KO</button>
          <button class="lang-btn" type="button" data-lang="zh" id="langZh">中文</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-head">
          <h2>Interview & Intake Matrix</h2>
          <p>A preliminary intake tool to identify whether a physician’s clinical work has been translated into a system and whether it is externally scalable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">

          <details class="section" open>
            <summary>1. Basic Professional Profile</summary>
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="fields">
                <div><label for="name">Name</label><input id="name" /></div>
                <div><label for="specialty">Specialty</label><input id="specialty" placeholder="e.g. Internal Medicine / Cardiology" /></div>
                <div><label for="subspecialty">Subspecialty</label><input id="subspecialty" /></div>
                <div><label for="position">Current Position</label><input id="position" /></div>
                <div><label for="institution">Institution</label><input id="institution" /></div>
                <div><label for="setting">Practice Setting</label>
                  <select id="setting">
                    <option value="">Select</option>
                    <option>Academic Medical Center</option>
                    <option>Community Hospital</option>
                    <option>Private Practice</option>
                    <option>Public Health / Government</option>
                    <option>Multi-site System</option>
                    <option>Underserved / Safety-Net</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div><label for="license">U.S. License Status</label>
                  <select id="license">
                    <option value="">Select</option>
                    <option>Full License</option>
                    <option>Training License</option>
                    <option>Pending / Future</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div><label for="board">Board Certification</label>
                  <select id="board"><option>No</option><option>Yes</option></select>
                </div>
                <div><label for="fellowship">Fellowship Trained</label>
                  <select id="fellowship"><option>No</option><option>Yes</option></select>
                </div>
                <div><label for="usYears">U.S. Clinical Experience (Years)</label><input id="usYears" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="foreignYears">Non-U.S. Clinical Experience (Years)</label><input id="foreignYears" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="diseaseArea">Core Disease Area / Public Health Problem</label><input id="diseaseArea" placeholder="e.g. cardiovascular disease, diabetes, cancer screening" /></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="section" open>
            <summary>2. Clinical Core</summary>
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="fields-3">
                <div><label for="patientVolume">Annual Patient Volume</label><input id="patientVolume" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="procedureVolume">Annual Procedure / Surgery Volume</label><input id="procedureVolume" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="complexVolume">Annual High-Complexity Cases</label><input id="complexVolume" type="number" min="0" /></div>
              </div>
              <div style="height:14px"></div>
              <div class="checklist">
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="clinical" value="high_risk" /><span>Manages high-risk or medically complex cases</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="clinical" value="multidisciplinary" /><span>Participates in multidisciplinary decision-making</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="clinical" value="rare" /><span>Handles rare, refractory, or difficult cases</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="clinical" value="triage" /><span>Improves diagnosis, triage, or treatment timing</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="clinical" value="critical" /><span>Provides ICU / emergency / acute care responsibility</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="clinical" value="consulted" /><span>Other physicians regularly consult this physician</span></label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="section" open>
            <summary>3. System Translation</summary>
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="checklist">
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="system" value="protocol" /><span>Created or improved a clinical protocol</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="system" value="pathway" /><span>Developed a clinical pathway / workflow / order set</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="system" value="screening" /><span>Improved screening / triage / referral structure</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="system" value="followup" /><span>Redesigned follow-up / discharge / care coordination</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="system" value="emr" /><span>Integrated into EMR / EHR / standard workflow</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="system" value="hospitalwide" /><span>Adopted beyond one physician or one-off case</span></label>
              </div>
              <div style="height:14px"></div>
              <div class="fields-1">
                <div><label for="systemDesc">Describe the main protocol, workflow, or system improvement</label><textarea id="systemDesc"></textarea></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="section" open>
            <summary>4. Scalability & Dissemination</summary>
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="fields-3">
                <div><label for="providersInfluenced">Number of Other Physicians / Providers Influenced</label><input id="providersInfluenced" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="sitesUsing">Number of Departments / Sites Using the Model</label><input id="sitesUsing" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="externalInstitutions">Number of External Institutions Affected</label><input id="externalInstitutions" type="number" min="0" /></div>
              </div>
              <div style="height:14px"></div>
              <div class="checklist">
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="scale" value="internal_spread" /><span>Used by other physicians in the same institution</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="scale" value="cross_dept" /><span>Applied across departments or service lines</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="scale" value="external_adoption" /><span>Adopted by outside hospitals or institutions</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="scale" value="training" /><span>Disseminated through training, CME, or formal teaching</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="scale" value="committee" /><span>Spread through committee, guideline, or network activity</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="scale" value="sustainable" /><span>System remains in place even without direct personal involvement</span></label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="section" open>
            <summary>5. Public Health / National Importance</summary>
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="checklist">
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="public" value="burden" /><span>Addresses a major U.S. disease burden</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="public" value="prevention" /><span>Improves prevention, early detection, or chronic disease management</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="public" value="access" /><span>Improves access for underserved or vulnerable populations</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="public" value="cost" /><span>Improves efficiency, reduces delay, readmission, or cost</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="public" value="hpsa" /><span>Works in HPSA/MUA/MUP or similar shortage context</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="public" value="community" /><span>Leads community outreach, screening, or navigation initiatives</span></label>
              </div>
              <div style="height:14px"></div>
              <div class="fields-1">
                <div><label for="publicDesc">Explain the national or public-health problem addressed</label><textarea id="publicDesc"></textarea></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="section" open>
            <summary>6. Research / Education / Translation</summary>
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="fields-3">
                <div><label for="publications">Publications</label><input id="publications" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="citations">Citations</label><input id="citations" type="number" min="0" /></div>
                <div><label for="guidelineStudies">Guideline / Implementation-Relevant Studies</label><input id="guidelineStudies" type="number" min="0" /></div>
              </div>
              <div style="height:14px"></div>
              <div class="checklist">
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="research" value="implementation_research" /><span>Research connects to real-world clinical implementation</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="research" value="guideline" /><span>Research is relevant to guidelines, policy, or practice standards</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="research" value="resident_edu" /><span>Teaches residents / fellows / medical students</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="research" value="cme" /><span>Provides CME, workshop, or formal external training</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="research" value="curriculum" /><span>Developed curriculum or skills-training system</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="research" value="translation" /><span>Education functions as a dissemination pathway for clinical practice</span></label>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="section" open>
            <summary>7. Evidence Strength</summary>
            <div class="inner">
              <div class="checklist">
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="protocol_doc" /><span>Protocol / pathway / workflow documents</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="policy_doc" /><span>Hospital policy / internal approval record</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="emr_doc" /><span>EMR / order set / implementation screenshots or records</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="metrics" /><span>Before/after measurable data</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="adoption" /><span>Adoption letters / usage confirmation from others</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="independent" /><span>Independent expert letters</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="committee_doc" /><span>Committee / network / public-health participation records</span></label>
                <label class="check"><input type="checkbox" class="evidence" value="grant" /><span>Grant / institutional support / QI project materials</span></label>
              </div>
              <div style="height:14px"></div>
              <div class="fields-1">
                <div><label for="evidenceDesc">Important Metrics or Evidence Notes</label><textarea id="evidenceDesc" placeholder="e.g. wait time reduced by 28%, colorectal screening increased by 19%, protocol adopted at 3 sites"></textarea></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-head">
          <h2>Initial NIW Assessment</h2>
          <p>Automated scoring is directional only. This public lite version intentionally limits attorney-level interpretation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <div class="score-grid">
            <div class="score-box"><div class="k">Clinical Strength</div><div class="v" id="scoreClinical">0</div></div>
            <div class="score-box"><div class="k">System Translation</div><div class="v" id="scoreSystem">0</div></div>
            <div class="score-box"><div class="k">Scalability</div><div class="v" id="scoreScale">0</div></div>
            <div class="score-box"><div class="k">National Importance</div><div class="v" id="scorePublic">0</div></div>
            <div class="score-box"><div class="k">Evidence Strength</div><div class="v" id="scoreEvidence">0</div></div>
          </div>

          <div class="report">
            <h3>Profile Type</h3>
            <p><span id="profilePill" class="pill warn">Not analyzed yet</span></p>
            <p id="profileSummary">Click Generate Analysis to display the initial classification.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="report">
            <h3>Executive Summary</h3>
            <p id="executiveSummary">Not analyzed yet.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="report">
            <h3>Strength Indicators</h3>
            <div class="reserved-box" id="reservedStrength">
              <strong>This section is reserved for attorney-level case structuring.</strong>
              Detailed strategic analysis requires a structured legal review.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="report">
            <h3>Risk / Weakness Indicators</h3>
            <div class="reserved-box" id="reservedRisk">
              <strong>This section is reserved for attorney-level case structuring.</strong>
              Detailed strategic analysis requires a structured legal review.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="report">
            <h3>Priority Strategy Notes</h3>
            <div class="reserved-box" id="reservedStrategy">
              <strong>This section is reserved for attorney-level case structuring.</strong>
              Detailed strategic analysis requires a structured legal review.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="note" id="noteText">
            This result is for preliminary structuring of a physician NIW case. The key question is not whether the physician is simply a good doctor, but whether the clinical work has been structured and scaled within a healthcare system.
          </div>

          <div class="cta" id="ctaText">
            If you would like a full case evaluation based on your inputs, please contact our office.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-note" id="footerText">
      This tool is for preliminary educational and case-screening use only. It does not constitute legal advice. © Law Office of Hong-min Jun.
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    const i18n = {
      en: {
